messages.content: What is nui-suite and how does it relate to ComfyUI?
nui-suite is a collection of custom nodes designed for ComfyUI, a GUI that uses a stable diffusion model to generate images and videos. It extends the functionality of ComfyUI.
What does the Dynamic Prompts Text Encode node do?
The Dynamic Prompts Text Encode node is a CLIP text encoder that uses Dynamic Prompts syntax.
What does the Feeling Lucky Text Encode node do?
The Feeling Lucky Text Encode node searches prompts on lexica.art based on the input and supports Dynamic Prompts syntax.
What is the purpose of the Output String node?
The Output String node is a simple node that sends a string from the backend to the frontend, and it is useful for inspecting a randomly generated prompt in the frontend.
